(8, 1, '2017-09-08 18:42:49', '2017-09-08 18:42:49', '<div class="about-text">\r\nContemporary dance, also referred to as Modern dance, is a mix of different genres. It came into existence in the early 20th century as a  revolt against the rigid techniques of Ballet. Since its artistic movements draw a visual representation of life, it is also known as “the dance of the day”.\r\n\r\nThe beauty of this dance form lies in the endless opportunities of exploring creativity since it does not have a set of defined rules. It gives an individual a sense of freedom by connecting his/her own mind with the body. Unlike other dance forms, contemporary allows the ease of energy flow and body movement. Since this form is highly versatile and compliments one’s natural body alignment, it is open for beginners as well.\r\n<ul class="contemporary-dance">\r\n<p><strong>Contemporary dance form can benefit you in many ways including:</strong></p>\r\n<li>- Opportunity to express own thoughts</li>\r\n<li>- Physical and Mental fitness</li>\r\n<li>- Knowing the techniques of using gravity</li>\r\n<li>- Versatility</li>\r\n<li>- Connect with emotions in a positive environment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSo what are you waiting for? Join our Contemporary dance classes in Yangon and connect with your inner self.\r\n</div>', 'Contemporary Dance', 'Contemporary dance form is the most artistic dance form. To put it across simply, it is a fusion of modern dance forms with Ballet. The moves involve full body swinging and a lot of sideways jumps. Come and learn some of the finest techniques under the guidance of best contemporary dance teachers at our center in Yangon.', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contemporary-dance__trashed', '', '', '2017-10-25 08:44:17', '2017-10-25 08:44:17', '', 0, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/yoga/?post_type=our_classes&#038;p=8', 0, 'our_classes', '', 0),
(9, 1, '2017-09-08 18:43:19', '2017-09-08 18:43:19', 'Bollywood dance can be best defined as a fusion of various Indian dance forms with a touch of western style performed on lyrics. At our center in Yangon, Bollywood classes are less like a course and more like an enjoyable and fun filled exercise. So come and groove like your favorite bollywood stars.', 'Bollywood Dance', 'Bollywood dance can be best defined as a fusion of various Indian dance forms with a touch of western style performed on lyrics. At our center in Yangon, Bollywood classes are less like a course and more like an enjoyable and fun filled exercise. So come and groove like your favorite bollywood stars.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bollywood-dance', '', '', '2017-10-12 06:08:38', '2017-10-12 06:08:38', '', 0, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/yoga/?post_type=our_classes&#038;p=9', 0, 'our_classes', '', 0),
