(227, 1, '2017-10-09 11:29:21', '2017-10-09 11:29:21', '<div class="about-text">\nOur Hatha yoga classes are an unmatched opportunity for people to learn practices acquired from traditional yogic forms that are still maintained in their full purity. Hatha yoga training will be organized and directed by some of the most skilled local and international practitioners.\n\nOur Hatha yoga training services and programs are not merely focused on improving physical fitness and strength instead, these programs offer a comprehensive process of naturally attaining a certain level of control over the mind and body. This control is what lets an individual to reach the state of joy, bliss and peace. These training programs conducted by our expert instructors at our studio in Yangon, Myanmar are just perfect for the individuals who’re struggling hard to deal with the hectic pace and stress of today’s world.\n<ul class="contemporary-dance">\n<p><strong>All the practices have been designed by our experts with a view to:</strong></p>\n\n<li-developmental clarity and focus,\n-improve vitality\n-balance the disturbed hormone levels\n-reverse the effects of ageing on the body\n-bring a sense of zest and fulfillment  \n</ul>\n</div>\n', 'Hatha yoga classes', 'Hatha yoga is a category that involves most yoga styles. The system of Hatha yoga includes the practice of postures and breathing exercises to bring peace to the mind and body. We have hatha yoga classes for all levels.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '218-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-10-09 11:29:21', '2017-10-09 11:29:21', '', 218, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/yoga/218-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(229, 1, '2017-10-09 07:23:07', '2017-10-09 07:23:07', '<div class="about-text">\r\nThere can be numerous reasons why people go to professional yoga classes. These reasons can be as different as the individual nature is but, yoga training should always be looked upon as an inward journey.\r\n<ul class="contemporary-dance">\r\n<p><strong>There are a great number of benefits which become strong reasons for joining a professional yoga class. Some of these benefits are:</strong></p>\r\n<li>- You get to learn about the right alignment of various poses – Working and learning under a professional yoga teacher will ensure that you get the proper alignment of poses in place</li>\r\n\r\n<li>- You will get the right physical assistance during the practice sessions – In case of difficulty while practicing a specific asana during the class, you can ask your yoga teacher to assist you in reaching the perfect pose for the asana.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>- You can get to learn ways to modify poses – With modifications, our body is supported in a better manner. These modifications to suit your body can be easily achieved under the guidance of an expert during a professional yoga class.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>- You will able to enhance your practice – Well, this one goes without saying. The more you practice under supervised guidance, the better results you get in terms of proper alignment of yoga poses.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>- You get to learn new skills – Well, practicing on your own can make your sessions repetitive and monotonous, whereas racticing in a yoga class can help you learn and explore new yoga skills.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNow that you’ve got ample reasons to choose a professional Yoga training class, go and find the most suitable one in Myanmar today.\r\n</div>', 'Reasons to choose professional yoga training classes', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'reasons-to-choose-professional-yoga-training-classes', '', '', '2017-10-09 12:27:48', '2017-10-09 12:27:48', '', 0, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/yoga/?p=229', 0, 'post', '', 0),
