(287, 1, '2017-10-13 11:50:06', '2017-10-13 11:50:06', '<div class="inner-pages">\r\n<div class="container">\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="row pdg-bottom">\r\n					<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-3">\r\n						<ul class="nav nav-tabs itinerary">\r\n							<li class="active"><a href="#Day1">Day1</a></li>\r\n							<li><a href="#Day2">Day2</a></li>\r\n							<li><a href="#Day3">Day3</a></li>\r\n							<li><a href="#Day4">Day4</a></li>\r\n							<li><a href="#Day5">Day5</a></li>\r\n							<li><a href="#Day6">Day6</a></li>\r\n						</ul>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=" col-xs-8 col-sm-9">\r\n						<div class="tab-content">\r\n								<div id="Day1" class="tab-pane fade in active day-scroll-prop">\r\n								  <h3>Day 1:</h3>\r\n								  <p>Arrive into Scotland and be met by one of our team who will assist you with your luggage and take you to your transport where you will be transferred to the Macdonald Marine Hotel - Poignantly positioned overlooking the wonderful North Berwick Golf Course and sea views of the firth of forth as well as the famous bass rock. Dinner will be arranged in one of North Berwick’s local restaurants </p>\r\n								</div>\r\n								<div id="Day2" class="tab-pane fade day-scroll-prop">\r\n								  <h3>Day 2:</h3>\r\n								  <p>After a Scottish breakfast you will take the short walk to the North Berwick Links.The West Links Course is a true links located on the edge of the Firth of Forth. It is a true championship course having hosted many events over the years.Playing the course is all about imagination with the sea in play on 6 holes! The beach is just one long and sometimes wet hazard if the tide is in. You will find walls in the middle of fairways and in front of a green. Dinner can be accommodated in the hotel , golf club or alternatively in one of North Berwick’s local restaurants .</p>\r\n								</div>\r\n								<div id="Day3" class="tab-pane fade day-scroll-prop">\r\n								  <h3>Day 3:</h3>\r\n								  <p>After breakfast you will take the short transfer to The Glen golf course where you will face a different test of golf. Scotland’s answer to the much heralded Pebble beach with it’s sea lined views - a course of great stature and an absolute must to play. As a special treat - We will arrange transportation to Edinburgh where you can spend the evening in Scotland’s capital city - enjoying the glorious sights of our capital city as well as sampling the local pubs and bars. We will also book you into one of Edinburgh''s most famous restaurants where you will enjoy some of Scotland’s finest cuisine.</p>\r\n								</div>\r\n								<div id="Day4" class="tab-pane fade day-scroll-prop">\r\n								  <h3>Day 4:</h3>\r\n								  <p>After breakfast, golf today will be played at Archerfield Links. A fairly new course built in 2004 but a wonderful test of golf with ‘gorse’ on almost every hole therefore requiring accurate and sensible tee shots. With Muirfield adjoining to this wonderful golf complex - this course has a lot to live up to and the overall experience is phenomenal. Dinner can be arranged at the course or in one of North Berwick’s excellent restaurants. </p>\r\n								</div>\r\n								<div id="Day5" class="tab-pane fade day-scroll-prop">\r\n								  <h3>Day 5:</h3>\r\n								  <p>After breakfast, golf today will be played at the world renowned Muirfield Links. A course that requires no introduction. A Tom Morris design and the number 1 ranked course in the area and ranked 3rd in Scotland. Impressively this course is ranked 9th from the top 100 golf courses in the world. This masterpiece is unlike any other links courses with two concentric loops on the inner and outer 9 holes meaning you experience all the dramas twice throughout your round. A course that has held 16 open championships and a true test of golf.</p>\r\n								</div>\r\n								<div id="Day6" class="tab-pane fade day-scroll-prop">\r\n								  <h3>Day 6:</h3>\r\n								  <p>After breakfast we will transfer you back to the airport in plenty of time for your flight back home and present you with a personalised gift compliments of Go-golf Scotland. </p>\r\n								</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Schedule', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '51-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-13 11:50:06', '2017-10-13 11:50:06', '', 51, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/yoga/51-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
