ce a different test of golf. Scotland’s answer to the much heralded Pebble beach with it’s sea lined views - a course of great stature and an absolute must to play. As a special treat - We will arrange transportation to Edinburgh where you can spend the evening in Scotland’s capital city - enjoying the glorious sights of our capital city as well as sampling the local pubs and bars. We will also book you into one of Edinburgh''s most famous restaurants where you will enjoy some of Scotland’s finest cuisine.</p>\r\n								</div>\r\n								\r\n								\r\n								\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Schedule', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '51-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-13 12:11:07', '2017-10-13 12:11:07', '', 51, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/yoga/51-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
